message.body: Seeing Dan off to the airport but I should be back here around 10:30. My friend Jane is in town and staying with me so let us know if you want to hang!
Hey, what are you guys up to?

hey hey! Jane’s actually on hold trying to get a new flight since all flights leaving today for boston have been cancelled, so our day opened up. Once we get done with that, we have were going to go grab something to eat at grindcore house with a friend who is vegan, but otherwise day wide open. I assume you don’t want vegan bagels in place of colin’s bagels (i know i wouldn’t...) but you’re welcome to join us there.
Id love to, i didnt wind up going up to fishtow
Fishtown*
ooh cool!
Do you know where grindcore is?
Nope, never heard of it
it’s at 4th and taker
let me check to make sure my friend is still planning to be there
because otherwise id be down for meeting somewhere else, they don’t have the largest food selection
Cool
oo ok she’s actually not able to hang out, glad i called
do you want to come eat brunch at the industry with us?
we’re tied to the phone right now, so if you want to come by here, we can just leave once we get done
Cool, ill head over in a couple minutes
great!
Hey thanks for hanging out. James going through a rough break up so its touch and go
*Jane's
So sorry we bailed.
It's alright, I'm sorry to hear that. Tell her that she's rad
And this place is super cool, i havent been hear since it was just a garage
Oh really? I had no idea it was ever so small. Yeah I love it there. And I'll send Jane your good vibes
